[img]http://api.ning.com/files/XNKY6NdKTUbMRxREzrj-LWTuics6f9i*e2i9b2h7QYmNyCNfBWy0mrnrEEIDN3RQ0mPP*D9nXas5d1dJC3CROV4CAXWuHw0b/Dota_allstars_5v5_by_kunkka.jpg[/img] I am starting a souce based on the warcraft 3 mini-game called dota (Defender of the Ancients)I Believe with a little help and touch i can turn a whole source into a who mini-game i dont exspect it to be perfect or glitch free.But im more then likley gona aadd other things to. but please be looking forward to this in the future. :D ill release a beta probly within time approx 3-7 months [size=20pt]UPDATE LOG[/size]
(8/1/09)[update] will be 508 should be able to use through umairscape(will be berky-scape based but im basicly gonna rewrite the who danm thing wish me luck :) (8/2/09)WILL BE BASED ON CWARS MAP THERE IS 3 LINE TO ENEMY'S AREA (8/3/09) add castlewars terrain and replaced hoping stones with terrain this was easier then i thought beta might be released a little bit earlier so far so good :) (8/20/09)NPC VS NPC ADDED!!!
[table][tr][td]Races added 4% done npc's atking each other :( 0% still finding a way to make them attack each other the most challanging thing ive had to do.[/td][/tr][/table] [b][i][u]NOTE:FOR THE SIMPLE MINDED FUCKTARDS LIKE AMERIKA WHO CANT EVAN SPELL HIS OWN COUNTRY'S NAME IM NOT PUTING WOW IN RS IM SIMPLY TAKING THE DOTA MINIGAME IMPLANTING IT INTO CWS SO WHAT IM BASICLY DOING IS MAKINGA CUSTOM CWARS WITCH IS GONABE A LITTLE FUNNER IM CODING THE SON OF A BITCH SO PLEASE [color=green]BE PATIENT :)[/color][/u][/i][/b]
